Metadata-Version: 2.1
Name: narator
Version: 0.1.1
Summary: Generate markdown work-reports from the body of github issues.
Home-page: UNKNOWN
Author: Mihai DincÄƒ
Author-email: dincamihai@gmail.com
License: MIT
Description: #### Usage
        
          - virtualenv --python=python3 sandbox
          - . sandbox/bin/activate
          - pip install -r requirements.txt
          - GITHUB_TOKEN=<auth-token-here> `python narator/narator.py <url-to-work-report-issue>`
        
        
        #### Example
        
        Issue description:
        
        ```
        Title 1
        
        todo create PR
        done investigate
        done discuss with team#1
        ```
        
        Output:
        
        ```markdown
        #### Title 1
          - DONE:
            - investigate
            - discuss with team#1
          - TODO
            - create PR
        ```
        
Platform: UNKNOWN
Description-Content-Type: text/markdown
